1
00:00:16,953 --> 00:00:18,789
- You poisoned us!
- You're right!

2
00:00:19,873 --> 00:00:21,541
I placed the ice!

3
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,920
I did that because she warned me

4
00:00:25,921 --> 00:00:27,798
that Madam Violet will harm you!

5
00:00:29,341 --> 00:00:31,426
That was the only way to save her

6
00:00:31,885 --> 00:00:34,096
without drawing suspicion
from Madam Violet.

7
00:00:34,638 --> 00:00:36,390
How do I know if I could trust you?

8
00:00:36,973 --> 00:00:37,973
Yes.

9
00:00:38,642 --> 00:00:40,769
I know I was a bitch to you sometimes.

10
00:00:40,852 --> 00:00:41,852
Sometimes?

11
00:00:43,021 --> 00:00:45,607
But I also want to get
out of this hellhole.

12
00:00:46,566 --> 00:00:48,026
I don't eat spinach.

13
00:00:49,111 --> 00:00:50,194
Just try it.

14
00:00:50,195 --> 00:00:51,238
One bite.

15
00:01:00,122 --> 00:01:01,122
Ace...

16
00:01:01,206 --> 00:01:02,206
Huh?

17
00:01:02,749 --> 00:01:03,749
Are you okay?

18
00:01:06,628 --> 00:01:07,628
Supremo

19
00:01:09,089 --> 00:01:10,215
are you okay?

20
00:01:12,676 --> 00:01:13,676
Thank you for the lunch.

21
00:01:14,553 --> 00:01:15,553
Zein.

22
00:01:15,595 --> 00:01:16,595
Are you...

23
00:01:16,972 --> 00:01:18,598
allergic to spinach?

24
00:01:19,683 --> 00:01:20,683
Stupid!

25
00:01:21,101 --> 00:01:22,686
You put Supremo in danger!

26
00:01:22,894 --> 00:01:23,895
You're such an idiot!

27
00:01:23,979 --> 00:01:24,688
Stupid!

28
00:01:24,730 --> 00:01:26,523
What should we do to her?

29
00:01:26,565 --> 00:01:28,190
Tie her up and punish her!

30
00:01:28,191 --> 00:01:29,191
Right!

31
00:01:29,276 --> 00:01:29,735
Tie her up!

32
00:01:29,735 --> 00:01:30,735
Zein!

33
00:01:31,528 --> 00:01:32,654
I promise you.

34
00:01:33,572 --> 00:01:35,574
They will pay for what they did.

35
00:01:36,867 --> 00:01:39,369
Black Blood Gang and Devil God Warrior.

36
00:01:40,328 --> 00:01:41,872
Memorize these faces!

37
00:01:42,456 --> 00:01:43,456
Next week

38
00:01:43,832 --> 00:01:44,958
they’ll be your target.

39
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,668
Happy hunting!

40
00:02:16,406 --> 00:02:17,407
Help!

41
00:02:18,408 --> 00:02:19,576
Help us!

42
00:02:22,162 --> 00:02:23,914
Are they afraid of me?

43
00:02:24,581 --> 00:02:25,832
Are they angry?

44
00:02:28,877 --> 00:02:30,378
Are they disgusted by me?

45
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:42,265
Do I really deserve this treatment?

46
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,271
Please.

47
00:02:48,271 --> 00:02:49,105
Nurse Cha, please.

48
00:02:49,105 --> 00:02:50,345
Something's wrong with Supremo.

49
00:02:50,690 --> 00:02:51,525
Stupid!

50
00:02:51,526 --> 00:02:52,691
You were so careless!

51
00:02:52,692 --> 00:02:54,152
Why don't you try thinking for once?

52
00:02:55,153 --> 00:02:56,153
Zein!

53
00:03:02,953 --> 00:03:03,954
More!

54
00:03:04,454 --> 00:03:05,454
More!

55
00:03:15,006 --> 00:03:16,675
Goodbye, Zein Shion.

56
00:03:18,301 --> 00:03:19,970
Zein!

57
00:03:32,002 --> 00:03:33,420
What do you think you're doing?

58
00:03:34,250 --> 00:03:35,250
Untie her!

59
00:03:36,183 --> 00:03:37,183
All of you

60
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,365
take my command.

61
00:03:41,337 --> 00:03:43,923
Nobody leaves this hall.

62
00:03:45,912 --> 00:03:47,913
This is an order

63
00:03:47,914 --> 00:03:50,250
from the highest
Supreme Student Government President.

64
00:03:50,837 --> 00:03:51,671
Understood?

65
00:03:51,696 --> 00:03:52,863
Didn't I say move?

66
00:03:57,272 --> 00:04:00,442
Don't ever cross their boundary.

67
00:04:02,741 --> 00:04:05,452
I said move and get out of my sight.

68
00:04:05,765 --> 00:04:07,392
We can't do anything!

69
00:04:07,684 --> 00:04:08,976
They're all heartless!

70
00:04:08,977 --> 00:04:09,977
Animals!

71
00:04:10,145 --> 00:04:11,313
You're just like them!

72
00:04:11,438 --> 00:04:12,480
You're a monster!

73
00:04:13,106 --> 00:04:15,150
You believe me, right?

74
00:04:15,567 --> 00:04:16,192
Do you?

75
00:04:16,359 --> 00:04:18,027
Do you believe in me, right?

76
00:04:18,028 --> 00:04:19,404
I didn't want to do it.

77
00:04:19,821 --> 00:04:21,948
Are you going to help us or not?

78
00:04:25,577 --> 00:04:26,369
Go on.

79
00:04:26,370 --> 00:04:27,370
Try me.

80
00:04:30,631 --> 00:04:31,631
Angelica!

81
00:04:32,145 --> 00:04:33,272
Stop it!

82
00:04:33,892 --> 00:04:34,892
Enough!

83
00:06:17,689 --> 00:06:20,108
They will never forgive me.

84
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:25,577
I understand if they won't.

85
00:06:25,602 --> 00:06:28,104
What happened to you was my fault.

86
00:06:28,551 --> 00:06:31,302
- No amount of apology can change that...
- Zein.

87
00:06:31,327 --> 00:06:32,579
What are you talking about?

88
00:06:37,417 --> 00:06:39,139
The students...

89
00:06:39,492 --> 00:06:40,743
they're avoiding me.

90
00:06:43,152 --> 00:06:46,030
I think that’s just their way
of showing respect to the Queen.

91
00:06:48,555 --> 00:06:50,569
A lot has changed when
you were unconscious.

92
00:06:52,711 --> 00:06:54,713
The campus security has doubled

93
00:06:56,225 --> 00:06:57,825
and all who were involved in hurting you

94
00:06:58,511 --> 00:06:59,553
are being punished.

95
00:07:01,441 --> 00:07:02,441
Supremo

96
00:07:03,276 --> 00:07:04,277
what's their punishment?

97
00:07:05,747 --> 00:07:07,332
I think it's better if you don't know.

98
00:07:08,856 --> 00:07:10,232
I think it's too much.

99
00:07:12,092 --> 00:07:13,092
Another thing

100
00:07:14,621 --> 00:07:16,664
Roxane isn't the queen of HU anymore.

101
00:07:19,210 --> 00:07:21,543
It's you now, Zein.

102
00:07:21,544 --> 00:07:22,544
Huh?

103
00:07:23,129 --> 00:07:24,129
How?

104
00:07:25,632 --> 00:07:28,259
I have to do it to them
to give you more respect.

105
00:07:30,261 --> 00:07:32,388
Now they won't be able
to touch you so easily.

106
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,140
Another thing.

107
00:07:37,446 --> 00:07:38,446
Matthew Hart

108
00:07:40,005 --> 00:07:41,173
is the new king.

109
00:07:46,236 --> 00:07:47,320
You seem happy, huh?

110
00:07:50,490 --> 00:07:51,491
I'll be back.

111
00:07:53,993 --> 00:07:54,993
I need to see Matt.

112
00:07:55,745 --> 00:07:58,331
- I haven't...
- You're not leaving me.

113
00:07:59,131 --> 00:08:00,131
Understood?

114
00:08:00,917 --> 00:08:01,918
I'm the Queen.

115
00:08:03,336 --> 00:08:05,046
And you know that
I don’t give a damn.

116
00:08:09,073 --> 00:08:10,393
Why do you keep focusing on Matt?

117
00:08:10,956 --> 00:08:11,915
Duh.

118
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:14,188
Of course he's my friend.

119
00:08:14,848 --> 00:08:19,269
And I had a crush on him first.

120
00:08:19,936 --> 00:08:22,204
But I'm the one you love.

121
00:08:22,229 --> 00:08:23,230
Are you sure?

122
00:08:25,692 --> 00:08:26,692
Why, Zein?

123
00:08:27,534 --> 00:08:28,657
Am I wrong?

124
00:08:32,866 --> 00:08:33,867
- Help me!
- Angelica?

125
00:08:35,050 --> 00:08:36,050
Angelica...

126
00:08:41,833 --> 00:08:42,876
Help...

127
00:08:43,318 --> 00:08:44,318
Nicky!

128
00:08:44,343 --> 00:08:46,352
I can't disobey my own decree.

129
00:08:47,964 --> 00:08:48,964
Stand!

130
00:08:49,322 --> 00:08:50,322
Don't worry.

131
00:08:51,342 --> 00:08:54,262
I told them not to put poison on the nail.

132
00:08:54,895 --> 00:08:56,437
Please!

133
00:08:56,462 --> 00:08:57,504
Have mercy on her!

134
00:08:57,529 --> 00:09:00,073
Please, Supremo! Please help her.

135
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,400
Please.

136
00:09:04,275 --> 00:09:05,317
You'll live.

137
00:09:06,977 --> 00:09:08,145
Supremo, please.

138
00:09:08,335 --> 00:09:09,419
Why are you being like this?

139
00:09:09,444 --> 00:09:10,779
Help her!

140
00:09:17,723 --> 00:09:18,807
Wait for me.

141
00:09:20,136 --> 00:09:21,212
Stand up.

142
00:09:21,237 --> 00:09:22,237
Come on!

143
00:09:29,273 --> 00:09:30,941
This is too much, Ace.

144
00:09:56,658 --> 00:09:58,742
Have you heard of Supremo's punishment

145
00:09:58,743 --> 00:10:00,078
to the ones who hurt you?

146
00:10:03,289 --> 00:10:04,415
I have.

147
00:10:05,625 --> 00:10:07,252
How do you feel about that?

148
00:10:10,191 --> 00:10:14,707
I honestly don't know
how I should feel about it.

149
00:10:24,292 --> 00:10:25,209
Stock room.

150
00:10:25,234 --> 00:10:26,234
Third cabinet.

151
00:10:26,259 --> 00:10:27,301
Faculty.

152
00:10:27,939 --> 00:10:29,107
Load sheets.

153
00:11:01,514 --> 00:11:04,350
That's why they're all afraid of me.

154
00:11:05,518 --> 00:11:07,478
Because of Supremo's punishment.

155
00:11:09,105 --> 00:11:11,357
I hope he won't be harmed because of this.

156
00:12:16,378 --> 00:12:17,421
Are you happy now?

157
00:12:24,555 --> 00:12:26,189
From being a newbie

158
00:12:28,188 --> 00:12:29,690
to becoming his secretary.

159
00:12:31,332 --> 00:12:33,418
And now you're fourth in the ranks.

160
00:12:35,108 --> 00:12:36,651
Now, you're the queen?

161
00:12:37,260 --> 00:12:38,844
Aren't you too greedy?

162
00:12:41,851 --> 00:12:43,127
You have everything!

163
00:12:44,257 --> 00:12:45,675
And you still want Supremo?

164
00:12:47,912 --> 00:12:48,912
Can’t you see?

165
00:12:49,539 --> 00:12:50,978
While you're beside him

166
00:12:52,166 --> 00:12:53,626
he gets weaker.

167
00:12:55,044 --> 00:12:56,712
You're making him weaker!

168
00:12:57,672 --> 00:12:59,424
You're a burden to him!

169
00:13:00,591 --> 00:13:01,759
I know!

170
00:13:04,337 --> 00:13:07,132
Do you think that makes me happy, huh?

171
00:13:09,217 --> 00:13:10,593
If Supremo is having a hard time

172
00:13:10,618 --> 00:13:12,411
I have a hard time too.

173
00:13:13,505 --> 00:13:14,881
But everything is your fault!

174
00:13:18,609 --> 00:13:20,319
If you didn't push your way into his life

175
00:13:22,029 --> 00:13:23,656
you wouldn't be having a hard time now.

176
00:13:25,116 --> 00:13:27,236
Both of you wouldn't be
having a hard time right now.

177
00:13:29,412 --> 00:13:31,497
Do you think I chose to fall for him?

178
00:13:33,541 --> 00:13:35,375
Do you really think that?

179
00:13:35,376 --> 00:13:37,003
It was all an accident!

180
00:13:45,595 --> 00:13:47,471
You won't get out of here even if you die!

181
00:13:47,472 --> 00:13:48,472
Angelica...

182
00:13:49,166 --> 00:13:49,939
- Angelica!
- Do you really think

183
00:13:49,964 --> 00:13:53,035
I would give up after
getting punished?

184
00:13:53,060 --> 00:13:55,646
I don't care how many nails
are stabbed through my body.

185
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:58,861
- Or how many cuts I get.
- Angelica!

186
00:13:58,886 --> 00:14:00,304
Why are you doing this!?

187
00:14:01,222 --> 00:14:03,908
I'll endure everything to protect Supremo.

188
00:14:05,865 --> 00:14:08,284
Do you think I wanted that to happen?

189
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:10,995
If you really love him

190
00:14:11,969 --> 00:14:13,429
stop hurting him.

191
00:14:14,874 --> 00:14:17,668
Do you think I wanted to hurt him?

192
00:14:21,589 --> 00:14:22,590
Angelica?

193
00:14:23,516 --> 00:14:25,267
Angelica!

194
00:14:32,808 --> 00:14:34,017
Please!

195
00:14:34,339 --> 00:14:36,841
Angelica, open the door!

196
00:14:38,648 --> 00:14:39,857
Please

197
00:14:39,982 --> 00:14:41,192
Angelica!

198
00:14:41,484 --> 00:14:43,277
Angelica, please!

199
00:15:14,058 --> 00:15:15,768
I'm not afraid of the dark.

200
00:15:16,852 --> 00:15:20,439
I prefer the dark more than daylight.

201
00:15:21,649 --> 00:15:24,777
In the dark, I can mask everything.

202
00:15:26,153 --> 00:15:27,280
I can cry,

203
00:15:28,322 --> 00:15:29,838
I can be weak.

204
00:15:31,265 --> 00:15:34,727
But in daylight, I'm forced to be strong.

205
00:15:35,347 --> 00:15:37,650
I need to face reality.

206
00:15:38,626 --> 00:15:40,461
You're ruining everything!

207
00:15:40,994 --> 00:15:42,953
What did I ever do to you?

208
00:15:42,978 --> 00:15:45,271
You didn't do anything
and you won't do anything

209
00:15:45,296 --> 00:15:47,422
besides leaving Supremo alone.

210
00:15:47,447 --> 00:15:49,323
You know the rules, Supremo.

211
00:15:49,348 --> 00:15:51,150
You should have just punished her!

212
00:15:51,175 --> 00:15:52,717
Ms. Kath is right.

213
00:15:52,742 --> 00:15:54,161
You'll lose your authority.

214
00:15:56,345 --> 00:15:57,721
I can live without this position.

215
00:15:58,787 --> 00:16:01,331
What is really your relationship
with Ms. Shion, Supremo?

216
00:16:03,571 --> 00:16:04,989
She's my secretary.

217
00:16:06,163 --> 00:16:07,455
I need to protect her.

218
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:09,439
And that's understandable.

219
00:16:09,572 --> 00:16:11,449
But your position is on the line here!

220
00:16:12,283 --> 00:16:14,869
We’re just concerned, Supremo.

221
00:16:15,184 --> 00:16:16,935
We don't want you to get hurt.

222
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,002
I don't care.

223
00:16:19,373 --> 00:16:20,833
I don't want to lose her.

224
00:16:21,792 --> 00:16:23,044
I need her.

225
00:16:26,531 --> 00:16:28,157
I know that you're aware
of the consequences

226
00:16:28,182 --> 00:16:30,476
of you helping them, Supremo.

227
00:16:30,944 --> 00:16:33,030
I will give them the exemption.

228
00:16:34,962 --> 00:16:38,298
You tell them that they can breathe

229
00:16:40,686 --> 00:16:41,979
for now.

230
00:16:46,567 --> 00:16:48,861
Lux started out this way.

231
00:16:49,654 --> 00:16:52,490
I am nothing like him.

232
00:16:53,991 --> 00:16:56,035
I need to choose when I get out of here.

233
00:16:56,911 --> 00:16:59,372
I can't remain in the middle of this.

234
00:16:59,997 --> 00:17:04,085
I need to choose a side and live with that.

235
00:17:14,185 --> 00:17:15,205
Zein?

236
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:25,481
Zein!

237
00:17:27,832 --> 00:17:28,832
Are you okay?

238
00:17:32,034 --> 00:17:33,160
Who did this to you?

239
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,200
Zein?

240
00:17:38,119 --> 00:17:40,454
It's okay. You can answer later.

241
00:17:41,359 --> 00:17:42,485
Let's get you to the clinic.

242
00:17:57,054 --> 00:17:58,054
Zein?

243
00:17:59,233 --> 00:18:00,233
Zein...

244
00:19:20,380 --> 00:19:21,380
I

245
00:19:22,442 --> 00:19:23,485
Ace Craige

246
00:19:25,726 --> 00:19:27,119
will be your shield

247
00:19:29,428 --> 00:19:31,638
your bulletproof vest

248
00:19:32,783 --> 00:19:34,493
and your knight.

249
00:20:02,805 --> 00:20:05,463
I can't fight anymore, Ace.

250
00:20:06,712 --> 00:20:08,088
You don't have to.

251
00:20:10,896 --> 00:20:12,606
I will fight for you.

252
00:20:28,330 --> 00:20:30,291
Always remember

253
00:20:31,167 --> 00:20:33,127
I'll always be here for you.

254
00:20:34,420 --> 00:20:34,920
I promise.

255
00:20:34,921 --> 00:20:36,881
I will never abandon you.

256
00:22:14,687 --> 00:22:15,980
What is it?

257
00:22:16,005 --> 00:22:17,131
What do you mean?

258
00:22:17,776 --> 00:22:18,776
Really?

259
00:22:19,066 --> 00:22:21,860
You really don't know?
Mia is she serious?

260
00:22:22,069 --> 00:22:23,278
You really don't know?

261
00:22:23,529 --> 00:22:24,612
Too bad.

262
00:22:24,613 --> 00:22:26,782
What a waste.

263
00:22:27,173 --> 00:22:28,384
Are you sure you don't know, Zein?

264
00:22:28,409 --> 00:22:29,450
Stop it.

265
00:22:29,545 --> 00:22:31,005
I don't know what you're on about.

266
00:22:31,326 --> 00:22:33,160
We won't tell you.

267
00:22:33,301 --> 00:22:34,635
She really doesn't know.

268
00:22:34,660 --> 00:22:35,908
Come on, guys.

269
00:22:36,669 --> 00:22:37,669
Please

270
00:22:38,053 --> 00:22:39,178
I have to get some things from my locker.

271
00:22:39,211 --> 00:22:40,796
Oh, okay.

272
00:22:49,828 --> 00:22:50,828
See you around.

273
00:22:51,724 --> 00:22:52,724
See you.

274
00:22:56,639 --> 00:22:58,015
Someone's blushing.

275
00:22:58,772 --> 00:22:59,982
Guys, stop it.

276
00:23:00,007 --> 00:23:01,759
So what were you talking about?

277
00:23:02,818 --> 00:23:04,194
Someone's blushing.

278
00:23:04,236 --> 00:23:05,486
What is it?

279
00:23:05,487 --> 00:23:06,739
You're annoying.

280
00:23:07,614 --> 00:23:08,240
Vanessa!

281
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,240
Zein, look.

282
00:23:09,825 --> 00:23:10,825
Supremo's there.

283
00:23:12,119 --> 00:23:13,995
There you are Dave and Jerome.

284
00:23:13,996 --> 00:23:15,204
I'm glad you're both here.

285
00:23:15,205 --> 00:23:17,082
Can you tell these two off.

286
00:23:17,700 --> 00:23:20,786
They're keeping secrets from me.

287
00:23:21,837 --> 00:23:23,505
Oh, you don't know?

288
00:23:24,246 --> 00:23:25,497
What is it?

289
00:23:26,959 --> 00:23:28,460
