Yes, I was alive but I wasn't living.

421
00:32:23,795 --> 00:32:25,380
Don't you understand?

422
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:28,300
For the longest time I’ve been here.

423
00:32:29,426 --> 00:32:31,011
I never felt alive.

424
00:32:32,887 --> 00:32:33,887
It’s like.

425
00:32:35,515 --> 00:32:36,850
It's like when I met you.

426
00:32:37,559 --> 00:32:38,935
I felt human again.

427
00:32:39,102 --> 00:32:43,148
Because of you I felt alive again.

428
00:32:44,316 --> 00:32:45,836
Like I finally learned how to breathe.

429
00:32:49,321 --> 00:32:51,781
We need to set each other free.

430
00:32:52,616 --> 00:32:54,117
It’s for the best.

431
00:32:54,257 --> 00:32:55,550
Fuck that, Zein.

432
00:32:57,078 --> 00:32:58,580
You're all I have.

433
00:33:00,294 --> 00:33:01,734
Please don't take this away from me.

434
00:33:02,417 --> 00:33:04,127
I need you more than what I have.

435
00:33:07,088 --> 00:33:09,174
You deserve what you earned.

436
00:33:11,136 --> 00:33:14,640
I don't want to be the reason
you lose everything.

437
00:33:20,060 --> 00:33:24,356
Darling, don't do this.

438
00:33:27,461 --> 00:33:39,461
Officail Main Site [www.kisskh.xyz]

439
00:33:29,486 --> 00:33:30,486
Please?

440
00:33:32,072 --> 00:33:33,740
