442
00:33:41,915 --> 00:33:43,375
You have my heart.

443
00:33:45,919 --> 00:33:47,003
Please don't leave me.

444
00:33:49,381 --> 00:33:51,383
I love you more than myself

445
00:33:52,133 --> 00:33:53,927
and everything that I have.

446
00:33:57,722 --> 00:33:59,302
So please...

447
00:34:00,225 --> 00:34:03,228
don't leave me hanging, darling.

448
00:34:22,706 --> 00:34:24,270
