449
00:35:12,005 --> 00:35:14,048
♪ Will a kiss ♪

450
00:35:17,050 --> 00:35:23,140
♪ grant me your affection? ♪

451
00:35:33,155 --> 00:35:35,407
♪ Do you know ♪

452
00:35:37,530 --> 00:35:46,466
♪ the nights beside you
still linger in my mind. ♪

453
00:35:54,078 --> 00:35:56,956
♪ My only wish ♪

454
00:35:57,634 --> 00:36:01,930
♪ please grant it even only in my dreams. ♪

455
00:36:06,421 --> 00:36:09,507
♪ I’ll take this as a chance. ♪

456
00:36:09,938 --> 00:36:13,483
♪ To give you all the time that you need. ♪

457
00:36:21,491 --> 00:36:24,452
♪ Darling ♪

458
00:36:25,119 --> 00:36:28,615
♪ how beautiful it is to love you. ♪

459
00:36:36,005 --> 00:36:41,135
♪ I will wait for your return. ♪

460
00:36:42,053 --> 00:36:45,890
♪ I’ll always be here. ♪

461
00:36:51,020 --> 00:36:53,982
♪ Darling ♪

462
00:36:56,987 --> 00:37:01,575
♪ how beautiful it is to love you. ♪

463
00:37:12,125 --> 00:37:16,337
♪ I’ll always be here for you. ♪

464
00:37:20,078 --> 00:37:23,248
Darling, I want to scream.

465
00:37:27,724 --> 00:37:28,808
Don't.

466
00:37:32,703 --> 00:37:34,079
I really hope you stop me

467
00:37:34,104 --> 00:37:36,398
