can hold it back anymore.

468
00:37:37,905 --> 00:37:41,033
I want to tell everyone
how I feel about you.

469
00:37:44,449 --> 00:37:45,474
Darling.

470
00:37:53,207 --> 00:37:54,375
I love you

471
00:37:55,668 --> 00:37:56,878
more than myself

472
00:37:58,250 --> 00:38:00,044
and everything that I have.

473
00:38:03,801 --> 00:38:07,013
Never ever leave me, darling.

474
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:27,116
What a scene.

475
00:38:35,917 --> 00:38:38,252
Can we stop with the theatrics?

476
00:38:40,088 --> 00:38:41,589
Glad to see you're still alive.

477
00:38:42,173 --> 00:38:43,633
