490
00:39:46,195 --> 00:39:47,447
Oh come on, Zein.

491
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:48,781
You can't fool me.

492
00:39:49,699 --> 00:39:50,575
Okay, fine.

493
00:39:50,669 --> 00:39:52,419
