498
00:40:15,725 --> 00:40:17,769
Nothing matters if you're not beside me.

499
00:40:21,856 --> 00:40:22,856
Zein...

500
00:40:25,443 --> 00:40:26,569
Darling?

501
00:40:27,929 --> 00:40:30,765
I want everyone to see us dancing together.

502
00:40:32,950 --> 00:40:34,911
It's one of my biggest dreams.

503
00:40:38,039 --> 00:40:39,039
Come on

504
00:40:40,166 --> 00:40:41,876
