524
00:42:02,582 --> 00:42:04,542
We don't need your opinion.

525
00:42:05,042 --> 00:42:06,419
We can handle her.

526
00:42:07,003 --> 00:42:08,003
Unless

527
00:42:08,462 --> 00:42:09,964
