528
00:42:11,507 --> 00:42:12,758
Relax.

529
00:42:13,970 --> 00:42:14,970
Fine.

530
00:42:15,469 --> 00:42:16,846
You said you can handle it.

531
00:42:19,331 --> 00:42:20,416
What's his problem?

532
00:42:21,517 --> 00:42:22,268
That's nothing.

533
00:42:22,269 --> 00:42:23,269
