545
00:42:55,249 --> 00:42:56,624
Well, sad to say

546
00:42:56,649 --> 00:42:58,818
this isn't love, my dear.

547
00:43:02,225 --> 00:43:03,059
Hold her.

548
00:43:03,060 --> 00:43:04,227
Let's go, Nicky.

549
00:43:05,144 --> 00:43:06,603
