551
00:43:07,939 --> 00:43:08,981
Hold her properly.

552
00:43:09,148 --> 00:43:09,815
I'm already holding her.

553
00:43:09,815 --> 00:43:10,650
Tighter!

554
00:43:10,650 --> 00:43:11,650
Fucking poison.

555
00:43:11,815 --> 00:43:12,815
I'm doing it.

556
00:43:12,985 --> 00:43:14,027
Do you think i'm fucking stupid?

557
00:43:14,028 --> 00:43:14,820
Can't you just help me?

558
00:43:14,987 --> 00:43:16,239
Don't hurt her!

559
00:43:22,411 --> 00:43:23,454
Matt!

560
00:43:24,364 --> 00:43:27,492
