who loves you the most.

571
00:44:04,829 --> 00:44:06,539
He'll wait for nothing.

572
00:44:40,740 --> 00:44:41,740
I got this.

573
00:47:31,535 --> 00:47:33,954
Do you know why I called you here?

574
00:47:35,164 --> 00:47:37,374
Because I can always rely on you.

575
00:47:38,209 --> 00:47:40,544
You're not like the others.

576
00:47:41,754 --> 00:47:43,380
We can see your worth.

577
00:47:46,550 --> 00:47:48,636
I need you to do one last thing.

578
00:47:50,679 --> 00:47:52,431
There's a war coming.

579
00:47:54,517 --> 00:47:56,435
And no one must know about it.

580
00:47:58,270 --> 00:48:01,690
Devil God Warrior and Black Blood Gang

581
00:48:04,119 --> 00:48:05,788
will remain blind about this.

582
00:48:11,784 --> 00:48:14,036
And you're going to
make sure of this.

583
00:48:14,995 --> 00:48:16,830
Can we rely on you?

584
00:48:20,459 --> 00:48:22,419
Don't you want to
get out of this place?

585
00:48:25,506 --> 00:48:27,215
To see your parents again?

586
00:48:27,216 --> 00:48:28,968
To be with them again?

587
00:48:29,927 --> 00:48:31,667
I'm the only one who
can give that to you.

588
00:48:32,846 --> 00:48:34,640
I'm the only one who
has the power.

589
00:48:38,769 --> 00:48:42,147
You chose the right guy, Madam Violet.

590
00:48:45,943 --> 00:48:46,944
Good boy.

591
00:48:52,366 --> 00:48:54,117
He's waiting for me.

592
00:48:54,118 --> 00:48:56,412
It's better for both of you
if you don't go to the party.

593
00:48:59,123 --> 00:49:01,667
Why are all of you
against our relationship?

594
00:49:02,126 --> 00:49:05,546
Supremo is planning to reveal everything.

595
00:49:07,631 --> 00:49:10,384
He's going to scream out loud
how much he loves you.

596
00:49:10,634 --> 00:49:12,011
If they're pushing through with it

597
00:49:13,387 --> 00:49:15,055
I'll handle Supremo.

598
00:49:15,598 --> 00:49:16,890
You know the rules.

599
00:49:18,142 --> 00:49:22,187
The SSG President is not supposed
to get involved with anyone.

600
00:49:22,563 --> 00:49:25,524
Having feelings for someone
won't do you any good in this place.

601
00:49:26,108 --> 00:49:27,651
It'll just be your weakness.

602
00:49:28,986 --> 00:49:31,363
You'll find the one for you.

603
00:49:36,118 --> 00:49:39,195
Why? Is there another Zein Shion?

604
00:49:39,246 --> 00:49:41,790
If you walk ten steps away from me

605
00:49:42,750 --> 00:49:44,630
just forget everything
that happened between us.

606
00:49:45,161 --> 00:49:47,038
Loving each other

607
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:50,382
was enough.
